<div class="banner_show" style="background-image: linear-gradient(-225deg, rgba(0,101,100,0.3) 0%, rgba(0,36,100,0.3) 50%), url(<%= image_path 'montagne2.jpg'%>); height: 40vh; background-size: cover;">
  <div class="banner-content">
    <h1>Propose your coworking and living space</h1>
  </div>
</div>
  <div class="container_flat">

    <div class="body_flat">

      <div class="content_flat">
        <div class="info">
          <div class="info_content">
            <h2> Welcome as a future host!</h2>
            <div class="pictures">
            <div class="our_photos">
              <%= image_tag "Host2.jpg", width: 180, height: 270, crop: :fill, id: "kudoz", class: "product-image hidden-xs" %>
            </div>
          </div>
            <h3> Earn money with Kikoho as a host </h3>
            <br> Propose a cowork and living place and optimize your revenues. Take the opportunity to meet new people coming from worldwide. Have unique experience and give a chance to new start up maybe to succeed. Be part of the adventure!<br>
           </div>
        </div>

        <div class="icone">
          <div class="icone_coworkers text-center">
            <i class="fa fa-home" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <p><strong> 1. Create your cowork </strong></p>
          </div>
          <div class="icone_room text-center">
            <i class="fa fa-envelope-open-o" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <p><strong> 2. Receive booking proposals </strong></p>
          </div>
          <div class="icone_coworkers text-center">
            <i class="fa fa-check-square-o" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <p><strong> 3. Validate booking proposals </strong></p>
          </div>
          <div class="icone_room text-center">
            <i class="fa fa-users" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <p><strong> 4. Get ready to welcome your host! </strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="host_value_proposition">
          <h3> <i class="fa fa-home" aria-hidden="true"></i><strong> 1. Create your cowork </strong></h3>
          <p>We have a bright and sunny north facing room available. It sleeps 2 people with a queen size bed and built in robe. <br>
          <br>
          Each room is equipped with its own key lock which allows for extra privacy during your stay.<br>
        </div>

          <h3> <i class="fa fa-envelope-open-o" aria-hidden="true"></i><strong> 2. Receive booking proposals </strong></h3>
          <p>We have a bright and sunny north facing room available. It sleeps 2 people with a queen size bed and built in robe. <br>
          <br>
          Each room is equipped with its own key lock which allows for extra privacy during your stay.<br>



      </div>

      <div class="container_form">
        <div class="form_flat">
            <div class="price"><h2 class="text-center"> Create your cowork space </h2></div>
            <div class="form-booking">
              <%= simple_form_for (@cowork) do |f| %>
              <%= f.input :city,  placeholder:"Paris" %>
              <%= f.input :address, placeholder:"16 villa gaudelet" %>
              <%= f.input :capacity, placeholder:"5"%>
              <%= f.input :price, label: "Price in US dollars ($)", placeholder:"50" %>
              <%= f.input :photos, as: :attachinary %>
              <%= f.button :submit, "create cowork", class: "btn btn-info form-control"%>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

